      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@\n+## \ud83d\ude80 Features\n+\n+### Add terminal theme\n+\n+Added a `terminal` theme for pi. Why?\n+\n+- Keeps pi aligned with your terminal's existing look.\n+- Avoids a mismatched color experience between pi and the rest of your terminal apps.\n+\n+How to use:\n+\n+```bash\n+pi install npm:@mavam/pi-terminal-theme\n+```\n+\n+Then select `terminal` in `/settings` under `theme`.\n+\n+*By @mavam.*"
    },
